      "x": 640,
      "y": 250,
      "width": 290,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "🏃 **Scrum** — 冲刺迭代"
    },
    {
      "id": "n002500000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 640,
      "y": 275,
      "width": 290,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "💻 **XP** — 结对编程/TDD"
    },
    {
      "id": "n002600000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 640,
      "y": 300,
      "width": 290,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "📋 **看板** — 限制在制品"
    },
    {
      "id": "n002700000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 640,
      "y": 325,
      "width": 290,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "🔧 **DevOps** — 开发运维一体"
    },
    {
      "id": "n002800000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 950,
      "y": 250,
      "width": 290,
      "height": 50,
      "text": "**敏捷四大价值观：**\n个体互动 > 流程工具\n工作软件 > 详尽文档\n客户合作 > 合同谈判\n响应变化 > 遵循计划",
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "n002900000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 640,
      "y": 370,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "## Scrum 三核心角色",
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "n003000000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 640,
      "y": 405,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "👤 产品负责人(PO) → 👤 Scrum Master → 👥 开发团队"
    },
    {
      "id": "g003100000000000",
      "type": "group",
      "x": 1280,
      "y": 20,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 440,
      "label": "📋 需求管理",
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "n003200000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1300,
      "y": 60,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "## 需求管理5过程",
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "n003300000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1300,
      "y": 95,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "① 需求获取 → ② 需求分析"
    },
    {
      "id": "n003400000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1300,
      "y": 120,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "③ 需求规格编写 → ④ 需求验证"
    },
    {
      "id": "n003500000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1300,
      "y": 145,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "⑤ 需求变更管理"
    },
    {
      "id": "n003600000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1300,
      "y": 185,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "## 变更控制流程",
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "n003700000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1300,
      "y": 220,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "申请（需求方）→ 评估 → 审批"
    },
    {
      "id": "n003800000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1300,
      "y": 245,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "→ 实施 → 验证"
    },
    {
      "id": "n003900000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1300,
      "y": 270,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "❗ 非所有变更需CCB批准"
    },
    {
      "id": "n004000000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1300,
      "y": 310,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "## 建模方法",
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "n004100000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1300,
      "y": 345,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "**传统：** 原型法 / DFD / UML"
    },
    {
      "id": "n004200000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1300,
      "y": 370,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "**敏捷：** Story / Backlog"
    },
    {
      "id": "n004300000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1300,
      "y": 395,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "**UML需求视图：** 用例+顺序+状态+活动"
    },
    {
      "id": "g004400000000000",
      "type": "group",
      "x": 1880,
      "y": 20,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 440,
      "label": "🧩 WBS 任务分解",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "n004500000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1900,
      "y": 60,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "## WBS = Work Breakdown Structure",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "n004600000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1900,
      "y": 95,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 50,
      "text": "对项目**由粗到细**的分解过程\n面向**交付成果**，定义**项目范围**"
    },
    {
      "id": "n004700000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1900,
      "y": 160,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "## 分解方法",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "n004800000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1900,
      "y": 195,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "📐 **自顶向下** — 整体→局部"
    },
    {
      "id": "n004900000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1900,
      "y": 220,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "📐 **自底向上** — 局部→整体"
    },
    {
      "id": "n005000000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1900,
      "y": 245,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "📐 **类比法 / 模板参照法**"
    },
    {
      "id": "n005100000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1900,
      "y": 285,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "## 关键要点",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "n005200000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1900,
      "y": 320,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "✅ 最低层 = **工作包**"
    },
    {
      "id": "n005300000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1900,
      "y": 345,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "✅ 工作包由**唯一主体**负责"
    },
    {
      "id": "n005400000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1900,
      "y": 370,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "✅ 表达式：图表/清单/树形"
    },
    {
      "id": "n005500000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1900,
      "y": 395,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "❌ 矩阵式不是WBS表达形式"
    },
    {
      "id": "g005600000000000",
      "type": "group",
      "x": 20,
      "y": 480,
      "width": 640,
      "height": 460,
      "label": "💰 成本估算",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "n005700000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 520,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "## 估算方法",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "n005800000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 555,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "📊 **类比估算** — 自上而下"
    },
    {
      "id": "n005900000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 580,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "📊 **自下而上** — 最细粒度汇总"
    },
    {
      "id": "n006000000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 605,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "📊 **参数估算 / 专家估算**"
    },
    {
      "id": "n006100000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 630,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "📊 **三点估算(PERT)**"
    },
    {
      "id": "n006200000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 350,
      "y": 520,
      "width": 290,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "## 功能点 IFPUG",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "n006300000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 350,
      "y": 555,
      "width": 290,
      "height": 50,
      "text": "**FP = UFC × TCF**\nUFC=未调整功能点计数\nTCF=技术复杂度因子"
    },
    {
      "id": "n006400000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 350,
      "y": 615,
      "width": 290,
      "height": 50,
      "text": "5类功能项：\nEI / EO / EQ / ILF / EIF"
    },
    {
      "id": "n006500000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 350,
      "y": 675,
      "width": 290,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "✅ 与编程语言和技术**无关**"
    },
    {
      "id": "n006600000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 670,
      "width": 290,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "## 关键公式",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "n006700000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 705,
      "width": 290,
      "height": 50,
      "text": "**定额估算：**\nT = Q / (R×S)"
    },
    {
      "id": "n006800000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 760,
      "width": 290,
      "height": 50,
      "text": "**PERT期望值：**\nE = (O+4M+P) / 6\nδ = (P-O) / 6"
    },
    {
      "id": "n006900000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 350,
      "y": 720,
      "width": 290,
      "height": 50,
      "text": "**单位换算：**\n1人月 = 22人天 = 176工时"
    },
    {
      "id": "n007000000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 350,
      "y": 780,
      "width": 290,
      "height": 50,
      "text": "**自制vs购买：**\n平衡点=(自制-购买初始)\n÷(购买-自制月维护)"
    },
    {
      "id": "g007100000000000",
      "type": "group",
      "x": 680,
      "y": 480,
      "width": 620,
      "height": 460,
      "label": "📅 进度管理",
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "n007200000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 520,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "## 网络图",
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "n007300000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 555,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 60,
      "text": "**ADM（双代号）**\n箭线=活动\n节点=代号/事件",
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "n007400000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 990,
      "y": 555,
      "width": 290,
      "height": 60,
      "text": "**PDM（单代号）**\n节点=活动\n箭线=逻辑关系",
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "n007500000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 630,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "## 关键概念",
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "n007600000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 665,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "⭐ **关键路径** — 决定最短工期"
    },
    {
      "id": "n007700000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 690,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "⏳ **虚活动** — 不消耗资源/时间"
    },
    {
      "id": "n007800000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 715,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "📈 **甘特图** — 条形图·显示起止时间"
    },
    {
      "id": "n007900000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 755,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "## 时间压缩法",
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "n008000000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 790,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "⚡ **赶工** — 增加资源"
    },
    {
      "id": "n008100000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 815,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "⚡ **快速跟进** — 并行执行"
    },
    {
      "id": "n008200000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 840,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "📊 **燃尽图** — 剩余工作量变化"
    },
