      "type": "text",
      "x": 1340,
      "y": 650,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "🔍 **质量控制**"
    },
    {
      "id": "n008900000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1340,
      "y": 685,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "## 敏捷质量",
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "n009000000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1340,
      "y": 720,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "📌 **测试左移** — 早期介入测试"
    },
    {
      "id": "n009100000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1340,
      "y": 745,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "📌 **测试右移** — 生产环境测试"
    },
    {
      "id": "n009200000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1340,
      "y": 780,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "## 人员角色",
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "n009300000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1340,
      "y": 815,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "👤 **业务分析师(BA)** — 需求分析转化"
    },
    {
      "id": "n009400000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1340,
      "y": 840,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "👤 **产品负责人(PO)** — 定义需求优先级"
    },
    {
      "id": "n009500000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1340,
      "y": 865,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "👤 **项目经理(PM)** — 计划与执行"
    },
    {
      "id": "g009600000000000",
      "type": "group",
      "x": 1880,
      "y": 480,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 460,
      "label": "⚠️ 风险与采购",
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "n009700000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1900,
      "y": 520,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "## 风险三要素",
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "n009800000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1900,
      "y": 555,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "**风险事件 × 发生概率 × 影响**"
    },
    {
      "id": "n009900000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1900,
      "y": 590,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "## 风险评估",
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "n010000000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1900,
      "y": 625,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "📊 **定性** — 主观评估"
    },
    {
      "id": "n010100000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1900,
      "y": 650,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 60,
      "text": "📊 **定量** — 盈亏平衡/模拟\n访谈/决策树/敏感性分析"
    },
    {
      "id": "n010200000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1900,
      "y": 725,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "## 应对策略",
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "n010300000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1900,
      "y": 760,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "🛡️ **回避** — 放弃高风险方案"
    },
    {
      "id": "n010400000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1900,
      "y": 790,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "📦 **采购** — 从外部获取/服务"
    },
    {
      "id": "g010500000000000",
      "type": "group",
      "x": 20,
      "y": 960,
      "width": 640,
      "height": 400,
      "label": "👥 团队与沟通",
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "n010600000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 1000,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "## 组织结构",
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "n010700000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 1035,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "🏢 **职能型** — 资源集中"
    },
    {
      "id": "n010800000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 1060,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "🏗️ **项目型** — 项目为中心"
    },
    {
      "id": "n010900000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 1085,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "🔀 **矩阵型** — 混合模式"
    },
    {
      "id": "n011000000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 350,
      "y": 1000,
      "width": 290,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "## 沟通管理",
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "n011100000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 350,
      "y": 1035,
      "width": 290,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "📢 渠道数 = n(n-1)/2"
    },
    {
      "id": "n011200000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 350,
      "y": 1060,
      "width": 290,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "🔄 20人 → 190条渠道"
    },
    {
      "id": "n011300000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 350,
      "y": 1085,
      "width": 290,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "💬 复杂问题→**口头沟通**"
    },
    {
      "id": "n011400000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 1130,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "## 敏捷团队",
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "n011500000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 1165,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "🏃 强调 **自组织** 形式团队"
    },
    {
      "id": "n011600000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 1190,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "📋 **Epic → Story → Task** 分解层次"
    },
    {
      "id": "n011700000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 1215,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "📖 **用户故事**：角色 + 功能 + 价值"
    },
    {
      "id": "n011800000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 1240,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "📝 **验收标准**写在故事卡**背面**"
    },
    {
      "id": "n011900000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 1265,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "📊 **Sprint Backlog** = 细化可完成Story"
    },
    {
      "id": "n012000000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 1290,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "🤖 **AI赋能**：计划/估算/跟踪/控制"
    },
    {
      "id": "g012100000000000",
      "type": "group",
      "x": 680,
      "y": 960,
      "width": 620,
      "height": 400,
      "label": "⚠️ 高频易错提醒",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "n012200000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 1000,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "❌ 瀑布模型不适合短期项目 → ✅ **适合**"
    },
    {
      "id": "n012300000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 1030,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "❌ 敏捷模型=预测+迭代混合 → ✅ 不是"
    },
    {
      "id": "n012400000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 1060,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "❌ 功能点与编程语言有关 → ✅ **无关**"
    },
    {
      "id": "n012500000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 1090,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "❌ 项目是为了创造重复产品 → ✅ **唯一**"
    },
    {
      "id": "n012600000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 1120,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "❌ WBS是对项目由细到粗 → ✅ 由粗到细"
    },
    {
      "id": "n012700000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 1150,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "❌ 所有变更需CCB批准 → ✅ 部分PM可定"
    },
    {
      "id": "n012800000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 1180,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "❌ WBS最低层=分到个人 → ✅ **工作包**"
    },
    {
      "id": "n012900000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 1210,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "❌ PDM箭线=活动 → ✅ ADM才是"
    },
    {
      "id": "n013000000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 1240,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "❌ 类比估算=自下而上 → ✅ **自上而下**"
    },
    {
      "id": "n013100000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 1270,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "❌ DevOps=自动化工具 → ✅ **文化+流程+工具**"
    },
    {
      "id": "n013200000000000",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 1300,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "❌ 甘特图显示关键路径 → ✅ 网络图显示"
    },
